snippet.textDisplay: Babul just poured his heart out right there! OMG what a song! Jeet was splendid as this composition had to be soft and melodious despite using those high notes and variations and he just nailed it. And yes use of shehnai was the masterstroke which gave song a sweet and enchanting touch. I bet very few musicians have that kind of understanding as what to use in a song to take it to the next level.
